column2: SELECT p.objID,p.ra,p.dec,p.dered_u,p.dered_g,p.dered_r,p.dered_i,p.dered_z,p.clean,p.flags,z.z as photoz,z.zErr as photozErr, s.specObjID as specObjID,s.z as specz,s.zErr as speczErr,   dbo.fPhotoFlagsN(flags) as note  from Galaxy  as p    LEFT OUTER JOIN photoz as z ON z.ObjID = p.ObjID LEFT OUTER JOIN specObjAll as s ON s.bestObjID = p.ObjID    WHERE        p.ObjID = #
